@@TJvAlignedEdit
<GROUP TJvAlignedEdit>
Summary
  Alignable edit control.
Description
  TJvAlignedEdit is a TEdit descendant that has an Alignment property to set the alignment of the
  edit control.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAlignedEdit.AboutJVCL
  <INCLUDE JVCL.Main.AboutJVCL.dtx>
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAlignedEdit.Alignment
Summary
  Indicates how the text should be aligned.
Description
  Alignment indicates how the text should be aligned in the edit window. Alignment uses the VCL's
  <EXTLINK borland://TAlignment>TAlignment</EXTLINK> type to indicate the alignment type.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAlignedEdit.SetAlignment
Summary
  Changes the edit's alignment.
Description
  SetAlignment set a new alignment for the edit control. After changing it the window is recreated.

  SetAlignment is the set method for the Alignment property.
See Also
  Alignment
